HotelClub WordPress Plugin

HotelClub WordPress Plugin provides a variety of widgets to search and display hotels.

INSTALLATION
------------

1. Upload "hotelclub" to the "/wp-content/plugins/" directory
2. Activate the plugin through the "Plugins" menu in WordPress
3. Go to "Appearance > Widgets" to configure your widgets

HOTELCLUB AND RATESTOGO AFFILIATE PROGRAMME
---------------

